1.12	The_Siege_of_AR-558	The Siege of AR-558	The Siege of AR-558 is the 158th episode of the television series Star Trek: Deep Space Nine, the eighth episode of the seventh season. The number 558 is also the production code of the episode. First aired November 18, 1998. It was written by Ira Steven Behr and Hans Beimler, and directed by Winrich Kolbe. The episode has an average rating of 4.7/5 on the official Star Trek website (as of August 21, 2007).	
